(- **Fresnel Lenses:** Lightweight concentric rings that approximate a convex lens) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Vergence-Accommodation Conflict \(VAC\):** In natural vision, the eyes both converge \(rotate) Tj
T*
(inward\) and accommodate \(focus\) to the same distance. Current VR displays fix the focal plane) Tj
T*
(at a single depth \(~2 m\), so the eyes converge at a virtual object's depth but accommodate to) Tj
T*
(the fixed screen distance. This causes fatigue. Light field displays and varifocal displays aim) Tj
T*
(to solve this.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 1.2.4 VR Software Pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(User Input \(HMD + Controllers\)) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(Pose Tracking + Prediction) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(Scene Graph Update \(Physics, AI, Scripting\)) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(Frustum Culling & Level of Detail \(LOD\) Selection) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(GPU Rendering \(Vertex Shader ? Rasterization ? Fragment Shader\)) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(Post-Processing \(Lens Distortion Correction, Chromatic Aberration\)) Tj
T*
(         ?) Tj
T*
(Display \(Left Eye | Right Eye\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
