(| Method | Input | Output | Best For |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Delaunay \(2D\) | 2D points | 2D triangles | Terrain, flat surfaces |) Tj
T*
(| Bowyer?Watson | 2D/3D points | Tetrahedral mesh \(3D\) | General purpose |) Tj
T*
(| Ball Pivoting | Oriented 3D points | Triangle mesh | Dense, clean scans |) Tj
T*
