T*
(**Post-processing the medical mesh:**) Tj
T*
(- **Laplacian smoothing:** reduces staircase artifacts from the voxel grid) Tj
T*
(- **Taubin smoothing \(?-? filter\):** smooths without shrinkage \(alternating positive/negative) Tj
T*
(smoothing steps\)) Tj
T*
(- **Mesh simplification:** reduce triangle count while maintaining shape) Tj
T*
(- **Hole filling:** fill any topological holes in the mesh) Tj
