T*
() Tj
T*
(**Dice Similarity Coefficient \(DSC\):**) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(DSC = 2 |A ? B| / \(|A| + |B|\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(where A = predicted region, B = ground truth. Range [0,1]; 1 = perfect overlap.  ) Tj
T*
(State-of-the-art BraTS results: DSC ? 0.88?0.92 for whole tumor.) Tj
T*
() Tj
