(**Hausdorff Distance \(HD95\):**  ) Tj
T*
(The 95th percentile of distances between surface points of predicted and ground truth meshes.) Tj
T*
(Measures worst-case boundary localization error.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Sensitivity / Specificity:**) Tj
T*
(- Sensitivity \(Recall\) = TP / \(TP + FN\) ? how many true tumor voxels are found) Tj
T*
(- Specificity = TN / \(TN + FP\) ? how many non-tumor voxels are correctly excluded) Tj
