(### 2.1 In-Circle Test \(orientation-aware\)) Tj
T*
(For CCW triangle \(A,B,C\), point D is inside circumcircle if determinant > 0:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(|Ax-Dx  Ay-Dy  \(Ax-Dx\)^2+\(Ay-Dy\)^2|) Tj
T*
(|Bx-Dx  By-Dy  \(Bx-Dx\)^2+\(By-Dy\)^2|  > 0) Tj
