T*
(- ln\(I/I0\) = -? mu\(s\) ds) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 4.2 Hounsfield Unit equation) Tj
T*
(HU = 1000 * \(mu_tissue - mu_water\) / \(mu_water - mu_air\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Anchor values:) Tj
T*
(- air ? -1000) Tj
T*
(- water = 0) Tj
T*
(- dense cortical bone up to +1000 or higher) Tj
T*
