(Real World <---------------------------------------> Virtual World) Tj
T*
(           |              |              |) Tj
T*
(           AR             MR            AV) Tj
T*
(      \(Augmented    \(Mixed Reality\)  \(Augmented      \(VR\)) Tj
T*
(        Reality\)                     Virtuality\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
