(## 9. Novel Rendering for VR/AR: NeRF and Gaussian Splatting) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### NeRF \(arXiv:2003.08934\)) Tj
T*
(Neural Radiance Fields -- photorealistic novel view synthesis:) Tj
T*
(- Scene = MLP neural network F\(x,y,z,theta,phi\) -> RGB + density) Tj
T*
(- Rendering: integrate color along rays via volume rendering) Tj
T*
(- Input: 20-100 photos with known poses) Tj
T*
(- Training: 1-2 days; rendering: 30s/frame \(slow\)) Tj
T*
(- View-dependent effects: reflections, specular highlights captured) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 3D Gaussian Splatting \(arXiv:2308.04079\)) Tj
T*
(Real-time alternative to NeRF:) Tj
T*
(- Scene = millions of 3D Gaussians \(position, covariance, color, opacity\)) Tj
T*
(- Rendering: project Gaussians to 2D, alpha-composite front-to-back) Tj
T*
(- Training: 30 minutes; rendering: 30+ fps at 1080p) Tj
T*
(- Application: Scan real space with phone -> photorealistic VR/AR environment) Tj
T*
() Tj
