54 738 Td
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5. Bowyer-Watson Algorithm \(O\(n log n\)\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The most commonly implemented Delaunay triangulation algorithm:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Algorithm Bowyer-Watson\(points\):) Tj
T*
(1. Create super-triangle S that contains all input points) Tj
T*
(2. triangulation = {S}) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. For each point p in points:) Tj
T*
(   a. Find all triangles whose circumcircle contains p:) Tj
T*
(      bad_triangles = {T in triangulation : p inside circumcircle\(T\)}) Tj
T*
(   ) Tj
T*
(   b. Find boundary polygon \(hole boundary\):) Tj
T*
(      boundary = edges of bad_triangles that are not shared by 2 bad triangles) Tj
T*
(   ) Tj
T*
(   c. Remove bad_triangles from triangulation) Tj
T*
(   ) Tj
T*
(   d. For each edge \(a,b\) in boundary:) Tj
T*
(      Add new triangle \(a, b, p\) to triangulation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. Remove all triangles sharing a vertex with super-triangle S) Tj
T*
(5. Return triangulation) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Complexity:** O\(n log n\) expected; O\(n^2\) worst case) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6. 3D Extension: Tetrahedralization) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In 3D, Delaunay triangulation becomes Delaunay tetrahedralization:) Tj
T*
(- Instead of circumcircles, use circumspheres) Tj
T*
(- No point inside any tetrahedron's circumsphere) Tj
T*
(- Used for finite element mesh generation \(FEM\)) Tj
T*
(- Libraries: TetGen, CGAL, Qhull) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7. Applications in Computer Graphics) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Application | Why Delaunay |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Point cloud triangulation | Connect nearby points without sliver triangles |) Tj
T*
(| Terrain meshing \(DEMs\) | Triangulate elevation data for terrain rendering |) Tj
T*
(| Finite element analysis | Well-shaped triangles for numerical stability |) Tj
T*
(| Voronoi diagrams | Dual graph for nearest-neighbor queries |) Tj
T*
(| Path planning | Visibility graph through triangulation |) Tj
T*
(| Interpolation | Natural neighbor interpolation on Delaunay mesh |) Tj
T*
(| 2D physics simulation | Good mesh for rigid body simulation |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 8. Limitations and Extensions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Limitations:**) Tj
T*
(- Does not work well with sharp features \(edges, corners\) -- quality near boundary can be poor) Tj
T*
(- Assumes points in general position \(no 4 cocircular points\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Extensions:**) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
