54 738 Td
(- **Constrained Delaunay:** Some edges are forced \(e.g., known boundaries\); used for terrain) Tj
T*
(with roads, coastlines) Tj
T*
(- **Conforming Delaunay:** Add extra Steiner points to make triangulation conform to input) Tj
T*
(edges) Tj
T*
(- **Weighted Delaunay:** Each point has a weight; circumcircle test uses weighted circles) Tj
T*
(- **Delaunay refinement \(Ruppert's algorithm\):** Adds vertices to improve triangle quality) Tj
T*
(\(minimum angle >= 20.7 degrees guaranteed\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
