54 738 Td
(**Asymptotic Decider \(Nielson & Hamann 1991\):** Test based on the trilinear interpolant's) Tj
T*
(saddle point to resolve face ambiguities.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Marching Cubes 33:** 33 topologically distinct cases \(instead of 15\) that guarantee) Tj
T*
(topologically correct meshes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7. 2D Version: Marching Squares) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The 2D analog: extract contours from 2D scalar field:) Tj
T*
(- 4 corners per "square" -> 16 cases -> 4 unique cases) Tj
T*
(- Used for: contour plots, 2D segmentation boundaries) Tj
T*
(- Simple and fast: O\(n\) where n = number of cells) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 8. Variants and Extensions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Variant | Innovation | Use Case |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Marching Tetrahedra | Decompose cube to 6 tetrahedra; no ambiguity | Alternative to MC |) Tj
T*
(| Dual Marching Cubes | Place vertices at grid centers; cleaner topology | Cleaner meshes |) Tj
T*
(| Adaptive MC | Non-uniform grids \(octree\) for efficiency | Large volumes |) Tj
T*
(| METABALLS | MC applied to implicit potential fields | 3D modeling |) Tj
T*
(| GPU-accelerated MC | Parallel execution on CUDA/OpenCL | Real-time reconstruction |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 9. Medical Imaging Pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(CT/MRI scanner) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(DICOM files \(512x512 x N slices, 16-bit integers\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Preprocessing \(gaussian smoothing, resampling\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Segmentation \(thresholding, U-Net, etc.\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(MARCHING CUBES at isovalue=0.5) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Triangle mesh \(STL, OBJ format\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Post-processing \(smoothing, simplification\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Visualization / 3D printing / Surgery planning) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 10. Performance) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Time complexity: O\(V\) where V = number of voxels) Tj
T*
(- Space: O\(E\) output triangles, E ~ V in practice) Tj
T*
(- Typical: 512^3 volume processed in ~1 second on modern CPU) Tj
T*
(- GPU: Real-time for 256^3 volumes) Tj
T*
