54 738 Td
(Dynamic tracking of Gadolinium bolus -> cerebral blood volume \(CBV\).) Tj
T*
(High rCBV = high vascularity = high-grade tumor.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**MR Spectroscopy \(MRS\):**) Tj
T*
(Chemical peaks in spectrum:) Tj
T*
(- NAA \(N-acetyl aspartate\) at 2.0 ppm: neurons \(REDUCED in tumor\)) Tj
T*
(- Cho \(choline\) at 3.2 ppm: cell membranes \(ELEVATED in tumor\)) Tj
T*
(- Cr \(creatine\) at 3.0 ppm: energy metabolism \(reference\)) Tj
T*
(- Lac \(lactate\) at 1.3 ppm: anaerobic metabolism \(necrosis/high-grade\)) Tj
T*
(- Lip \(lipids\): necrotic tumor) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Elevated Cho/NAA ratio > 2.0** strongly suggests high-grade glioma.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 3. CT vs MRI Comparison) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Aspect | CT | MRI |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Physical principle | X-ray attenuation | NMR of protons |) Tj
T*
(| Radiation | Ionizing \(X-rays\) | Non-ionizing \(RF + magnets\) |) Tj
T*
(| Acquisition time | 5-60 seconds | 20-60 minutes |) Tj
T*
(| Resolution | 0.5-1mm isotropic | 1-3mm typical |) Tj
T*
(| Bone/calcification | Excellent | Poor \(no signal\) |) Tj
T*
(| Soft tissue | Moderate | Excellent |) Tj
T*
(| Hemorrhage \(acute\) | Bright \(hyperdense\) | Depends on sequence |) Tj
T*
(| Brain tumors | Shows mass, edema | Shows tumor sub-regions |) Tj
T*
(| Stroke | Early: often normal; late: hypodense | DWI: bright within minutes |) Tj
T*
(| Cost | Lower | Higher |) Tj
T*
(| Main limitation | Radiation dose | Slow, contraindications \(metal\) |) Tj
T*
(| Claustrophobia | Rare | Common |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4. 3D Reconstruction Pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(DICOM files \(512x512 x N slices\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Read with pydicom/SimpleITK -> numpy array) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Preprocessing:) Tj
T*
(  - Normalize HU values) Tj
T*
(  - Resample to isotropic voxel spacing \(e.g., 1mm x 1mm x 1mm\)) Tj
T*
(  - Apply Gaussian smoothing \(sigma=0.5-1.0\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Segmentation:) Tj
T*
(  - Thresholding \(Otsu\) or) Tj
T*
(  - Region growing or) Tj
T*
(  - Deep learning \(U-Net, nnU-Net\)) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
(    v) Tj
T*
(Marching Cubes \(isovalue = 0.5\)) Tj
T*
(  -> Triangle mesh) Tj
T*
(    |) Tj
T*
