T*
(### Transformer-Based Methods) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(TransBTS \(MICCAI 2021\):) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(3D CNN encoder -> flatten spatial features to sequence) Tj
T*
(                -> Transformer encoder \(multi-head self-attention\)) Tj
T*
(                -> CNN decoder with skip connections) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Self-attention captures long-range dependencies \(critical for irregular tumor shapes\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(SwinUNETR \(CVPR 2022\):) Tj
T*
(- Hierarchical Swin Transformer backbone \(arXiv:2103.14030\)) Tj
T*
(- Shifted Window self-attention: linear complexity w.r.t. volume size) Tj
T*
(- Pretraining on large unlabeled medical datasets) Tj
T*
(- State-of-the-art on BraTS 2021) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5. Automated Brain Tumor Analysis Pipeline) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
