BT
/F1 9 Tf
11 TL
54 738 Td
(## 2. Bernstein Basis Polynomials) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The building blocks of Bzier curves:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
($$B_{i,n}\(t\) = \\binom{n}{i} t^i \(1-t\)^{n-i}, \\quad t \\in [0,1]$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Key properties \(MEMORIZE\):**) Tj
T*
(- Sum to 1: $\\sum_{i=0}^n B_{i,n}\(t\) = 1$) Tj
T*
(- Non-negative: $B_{i,n}\(t\) \\geq 0$) Tj
T*
(- Maximum at $t = i/n$) Tj
T*
(- Symmetry: $B_{i,n}\(t\) = B_{n-i,n}\(1-t\)$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Values at endpoints:**) Tj
T*
(- $B_{0,n}\(0\) = 1$, all others = 0 at t=0) Tj
T*
(- $B_{n,n}\(1\) = 1$, all others = 0 at t=1) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 3. The Bzier Curve Formula) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
($$\\boxed{B\(t\) = \\sum_{i=0}^{n} \\binom{n}{i} \(1-t\)^{n-i} t^i \\cdot P_i}$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4. Specific Degrees) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Degree 1 \(Linear\) ? 2 points) Tj
T*
($$B\(t\) = \(1-t\)P_0 + t\\,P_1$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Degree 2 \(Quadratic\) ? 3 points) Tj
T*
($$B\(t\) = \(1-t\)^2 P_0 + 2t\(1-t\)P_1 + t^2 P_2$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Coefficients: 1, 2, 1**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Degree 3 \(Cubic\) ? 4 points ? MOST COMMON ?) Tj
T*
($$B\(t\) = \(1-t\)^3 P_0 + 3t\(1-t\)^2 P_1 + 3t^2\(1-t\) P_2 + t^3 P_3$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Coefficients: 1, 3, 3, 1**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Degree 4 \(Quartic\) ? 5 points) Tj
T*
($$B\(t\) = \(1-t\)^4 P_0 + 4t\(1-t\)^3 P_1 + 6t^2\(1-t\)^2 P_2 + 4t^3\(1-t\) P_3 + t^4 P_4$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Coefficients: 1, 4, 6, 4, 1**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Degree 5 \(Quintic\) ? 6 points) Tj
T*
($$B\(t\) = \(1-t\)^5 P_0 + 5t\(1-t\)^4 P_1 + 10t^2\(1-t\)^3 P_2 + 10t^3\(1-t\)^2 P_3 + 5t^4\(1-t\) P_4 +) Tj
T*
(t^5 P_5$$) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Coefficients: 1, 5, 10, 10, 5, 1**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5. Pascal's Triangle \(Binomial Coefficients Lookup\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(n=0:          1) Tj
T*
(n=1:        1   1) Tj
T*
(n=2:      1   2   1) Tj
T*
(n=3:    1   3   3   1) Tj
T*
(n=4:  1   4   6   4   1) Tj
T*
(n=5: 1   5  10  10   5   1) Tj
T*
(n=6: 1   6  15  20  15   6   1) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
