(## 3. Triangle Scheme for Hand Computation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This is how to organize your work on paper. Draw a triangle and fill left-to-right:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Level j=0    j=1       j=2       j=3) Tj
T*
(?????????????????????????????????????????????????????) Tj
T*
(P0^\(0\)) Tj
T*
(           P0^\(1\)) Tj
T*
(P1^\(0\)               P0^\(2\)) Tj
T*
(           P1^\(1\)               P0^\(3\)  <-- ANSWER) Tj
T*
(P2^\(0\)               P1^\(2\)) Tj
T*
(           P2^\(1\)) Tj
T*
(P3^\(0\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Each entry = \(1-t\) * entry_above_left  +  t * entry_below_left**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For a QUADRATIC \(3 points, 2 rounds\):) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(P0^\(0\)) Tj
T*
(           P0^\(1\)) Tj
T*
(P1^\(0\)               P0^\(2\)  <-- ANSWER) Tj
T*
(           P1^\(1\)) Tj
T*
(P2^\(0\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4. Complete Worked Examples) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Example A: Quadratic at t = 0.5) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Given: P0=\(0,0\), P1=\(2,4\), P2=\(4,0\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Level 0:  \(0,0\)      \(2,4\)      \(4,0\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Level 1:) Tj
T*
(  Q0 = 0.5*\(0,0\) + 0.5*\(2,4\) = \(0,0\)+\(1,2\) = \(1, 2\)) Tj
T*
(  Q1 = 0.5*\(2,4\) + 0.5*\(4,0\) = \(1,2\)+\(2,0\) = \(3, 2\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Level 2:) Tj
T*
(  R0 = 0.5*\(1,2\) + 0.5*\(3,2\) = \(0.5,1\)+\(1.5,1\) = \(2, 2\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(ANSWER: B\(0.5\) = \(2, 2\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Verify: \(1/4\)\(0,0\) + \(2/4\)\(2,4\) + \(1/4\)\(4,0\) = \(0+1+1, 0+2+0\) = \(2,2\) CORRECT) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
