(## 5. Mental Math Shortcuts) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**For t = 0.5:** Every step is just averaging adjacent pairs. Fastest computation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**For t = 1/3:** Use fractions 2/3 and 1/3. Keep exact fractions throughout.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**For t = 3/4:** Use fractions 1/4 and 3/4. Denominators build up as powers of 4.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Check:** At t=0 the answer should be P0; at t=1 it should be Pn. Use this to verify) Tj
T*
(direction.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6. Common Mistakes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. **Wrong order of blending:** It's \(1-t\)*left + t*right, NOT t*left + \(1-t\)*right) Tj
T*
(2. **Forgetting to do n rounds:** n+1 points needs n rounds \(a cubic with 4 points needs 3) Tj
T*
(rounds\)) Tj
T*
(3. **Wrong triangle structure:** Each round has one fewer point than the previous) Tj
T*
(4. **Not verifying at t=0 or t=1:** Quick sanity check) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
