() Tj
T*
(## 4. Full Worked Example: Bilinear Patch \(degree 1,1\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4 control points:) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(P00=\(0,0,0\)   P01=\(1,0,1\)) Tj
T*
(P10=\(0,1,1\)   P11=\(1,1,0\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Evaluate at \(u,v\) = \(0.5, 0.5\):) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Stage 1 \(fix u=0.5, evaluate rows in u-direction... or v-direction first\):**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Actually let us fix v=0.5 and evaluate each row in v:) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Q0\(0.5\) = B_{0,1}\(0.5\)*P00 + B_{1,1}\(0.5\)*P01) Tj
T*
(        = 0.5*\(0,0,0\) + 0.5*\(1,0,1\)) Tj
T*
(        = \(0.5, 0, 0.5\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Q1\(0.5\) = 0.5*P10 + 0.5*P11) Tj
T*
(        = 0.5*\(0,1,1\) + 0.5*\(1,1,0\)) Tj
T*
(        = \(0.5, 1.0, 0.5\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Stage 2 \(evaluate Q0, Q1 in u at u=0.5\):**) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(B\(0.5,0.5\) = 0.5*Q0\(0.5\) + 0.5*Q1\(0.5\)) Tj
T*
(           = 0.5*\(0.5,0,0.5\) + 0.5*\(0.5,1,0.5\)) Tj
T*
(           = \(0.25,0,0.25\) + \(0.25,0.5,0.25\)) Tj
T*
(           = \(0.5, 0.5, 0.5\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(ANSWER: B\(0.5,0.5\) = \(0.5, 0.5, 0.5\) -- center of patch.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 5. Full Worked Example: Biquadratic Patch \(degree 2,2\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(9 control points \(3x3 grid\):) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
(Row 0 \(i=0\): P00=\(0,0,0\)  P01=\(1,0,1\)  P02=\(2,0,0\)) Tj
T*
(Row 1 \(i=1\): P10=\(0,1,1\)  P11=\(1,1,2\)  P12=\(2,1,1\)) Tj
T*
(Row 2 \(i=2\): P20=\(0,2,0\)  P21=\(1,2,1\)  P22=\(2,2,0\)) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Evaluate at \(u,v\) = \(0.5, 0.5\):) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Bernstein quadratic at t=0.5: B_{0,2}=0.25, B_{1,2}=0.50, B_{2,2}=0.25) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Stage 1: Fix v=0.5, evaluate each row in v:**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Row 0: Q0 = 0.25*\(0,0,0\) + 0.50*\(1,0,1\) + 0.25*\(2,0,0\)) Tj
T*
(           = \(0,0,0\)+\(0.5,0,0.5\)+\(0.5,0,0\) = \(1.0, 0.0, 0.5\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Row 1: Q1 = 0.25*\(0,1,1\) + 0.50*\(1,1,2\) + 0.25*\(2,1,1\)) Tj
T*
(           = \(0,0.25,0.25\)+\(0.5,0.5,1.0\)+\(0.5,0.25,0.25\) = \(1.0, 1.0, 1.5\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
