(## 6. Properties) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Property | Explanation |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| Corner interpolation | P00,P0n,Pm0,Pmn lie ON the surface |) Tj
T*
(| Boundary curves | Each boundary is a Bezier curve using boundary row/column |) Tj
T*
(| Tangent at \(0,0\) in u | partial B/partial u = m*\(P10 - P00\) |) Tj
T*
(| Tangent at \(0,0\) in v | partial B/partial v = n*\(P01 - P00\) |) Tj
T*
(| Normal at corner | \(partial u\) x \(partial v\) |) Tj
T*
(| Convex hull | Entire surface lies in convex hull of all control points |) Tj
T*
(| Affine invariance | Transform control points = transform surface |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
