(## 7. Partial Derivatives for Surface Normals) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For bicubic \(m=n=3\):) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(partial B/partial u \(u,v\) = 3 * Sum_{i=0}^{2} Sum_{j=0}^{3}) Tj
T*
(B_{i,2}\(u\)*B_{j,3}\(v\)*\(P_{i+1,j}-P_{i,j}\)) Tj
T*
(partial B/partial v \(u,v\) = 3 * Sum_{i=0}^{3} Sum_{j=0}^{2}) Tj
T*
(B_{i,3}\(u\)*B_{j,2}\(v\)*\(P_{i,j+1}-P_{i,j}\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Surface normal: N = \(partial B/partial u\) x \(partial B/partial v\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
